Title: 'Motorcycle trip to highlands of Ladakh '
DateModified: '2018-02-16'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/motorcycle-trip-to-highlands-of-ladakh
SetInCountry: India
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Umesh  Walia
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "I Umesh Walia and my 7 friends decided to explore the Himalayas in June 2016,\
  \ on our motorcycles ! We all friends have one thing in common the passion of motorized\
  \ machines to explore the new destinations each time ! \nDay one : we started early\
  \ from lucknow at around 6:30 am . It\u2019s very hot in India in June month! After\
  \ riding around twelve hours with short breaks to avoid dehydration n heat strokes\
  \ we reach Sonipat in evening almost stretch of 560 kilometers ! \nDay two: woke\
  \ up around 7 am , again geared up for next 500 kilometers. So had breakfast n left\
  \ for pathankot n reached in night after a hectic hot day! Made halt n find a local\
  \ restaurant with excellent Mughalai cuisine ! had a delicious dinner ! \nDay three:\
  \ from pathankot we started late because of one motorcycle fuel tank was leaking\
  \ ! After fixing it we left for next destination ! After loosing 3 hours in morning\
  \ we reached a famous hill station called patni top ! \n\nIt\u2019s a 14 day travel\
  \ on motorcycles covering 4400 kilometers \nWith accident n bad weather \nWill write\
  \ with full details if given chance"
